00036     template <typename ExpressionType>
00037     struct optimize_impl
00038     {
00039       //default: no optimization available, thus don't manipulate anything
00040       enum { value = 0 };
00041       typedef ExpressionType        type;
00042     };
00043     
00044     template <typename LHS, typename OP, typename RHS>
00045     struct optimize_impl< ct_binary_expr<LHS, OP, RHS> >
00046     {
00047       //default: no optimization available, thus don't manipulate anything
00048       enum { value = optimize_impl<LHS>::value + optimize_impl<RHS>::value };
00049       typedef ct_binary_expr<typename optimize_impl<LHS>::type,
00050                              OP,
00051                              typename optimize_impl<RHS>::type
00052                             >        type;
00053     };
